                            <span class="current">Making Payments</span>
                        </nav>
                        <!-- Page Title -->
                        <h1 class="cmp-page-title" id="cmp_title">Making Payments</h1>
                        <p class="cmp-page-subtitle">
          Learn how to make fast, secure payments using the MPay Consumer Wallet. Whether scanning a QR code, showing yours, or tapping with NFC — paying has never been easier. </p>
                        <!-- Payment Method Cards -->
                        <div class="cmp-method-cards">
                            <div class="cmp-method-card">
                                <div class="cmp-method-card-icon">
                                    <i class="fa fa-qrcode"></i>
                                </div>
                                <h5>QR Code Payments</h5>
                                <p>Scan or show a QR code to complete payments instantly at any MPay merchant.</p>
                            </div>
                            <div class="cmp-method-card">
                                <div class="cmp-method-card-icon">
                                    <i class="fa fa-wifi"></i>
                                </div>
                                <h5>NFC Tap-to-Pay</h5>
                                <p>Simply hold your phone near the terminal for a contactless payment experience.</p>
                            </div>
                        </div>
                        <!-- Section: Scanning QR Codes -->
                        <section class="cmp-section" id="cmp_content_scan_qr">
                            <h2 class="cmp-section-title" id="scan-qr">Scanning QR Codes</h2>
                            <p>The most common way to pay is by scanning a merchant's QR code. This process takes only a few seconds and securely processes your payment through the MPay network.</p>
                            <h4>How to do a Scan to Pay</h4>
                            <p><b>Scan to Pay</b> allows users to scan a QR code to quickly send money or make payments using their wallet.</p>
                            <div class="steps">
                                <div class="step">
                                    <div class="step-title">Tap &quot;Scan to Pay&quot;</div>
                                    <div class="step-content">From the home screen, tap the <strong>Scan to Pay icon</strong> in the <b>Send Money</b> section.
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="step">
                                    <div class="step-title">Scan the Recipient's QR Code</div>
                                    <div class="step-content">Point your camera at the recipient&apos;s QR code. Once scanned, the recipient&apos;s details will automatically populated in Scan to Pay form.&nbsp;</div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="step">
                                    <div class="step-title">Enter Amount and Confirm</div>
                                    <div class="step-content">Enter the transfer amount, review the details, and confirm with your PIN or biometric authentication.</div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="step">
                                    <div class="step-title">Transfer Complete</div>
                                    <div class="step-content">You&apos;ll see a confirmation screen with a transaction <b>reference number.</b>&nbsp;
                                        <p>The recipient is notified instantly.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <ol class="cmp-steps">
</ol>
                            <!-- QR Scanner Visual -->
                            <div class="cmp-qr-visual" aria-hidden="true">
                                <div class="cmp-phone-mockup">
                                    <div class="cmp-phone-screen">
                                        <div class="cmp-phone-notch"></div>
                                        <div class="cmp-qr-scanner">
                                            <div class="cmp-qr-corner top-left"></div>
                                            <div class="cmp-qr-corner top-right"></div>
                                            <div class="cmp-qr-corner bottom-left"></div>
                                            <div class="cmp-qr-corner bottom-right"></div>
                                            <div class="cmp-qr-scan-line"></div>
                                        </div>
                                        <div class="cmp-qr-label">Align QR code within frame</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="cmp-callout info">
                                <div class="cmp-callout-icon">
                                    <i class="fa fa-info-circle"></i>
                                </div>
                                <div class="cmp-callout-body">
                                    <strong>Tip: Quick Pay Shortcut</strong>
                                    <p>You can also launch the QR scanner directly by double-tapping the MPay icon on your home screen, or by using the "Scan" shortcut from the notification shade widget.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </section>
                        <!-- Section: Showing Your QR Code -->
                        <section class="cmp-section" id="cmp_content_show_qr">
                            <h2 class="cmp-section-title" id="show-qr">Showing Your QR Code</h2>
                            <p>Some merchants prefer to scan your QR code using their terminal or device. In this case, you simply present your personal payment QR code for them to scan.</p>
                            <h4>How to Show Your QR</h4>
                            <ol class="cmp-steps">
                                <li class="cmp-step">
                                    <div class="cmp-step-number">1</div>
                                    <div class="cmp-step-content">
                                        <h5>Open Your Payment Code</h5>
                                        <p>Tap <strong>"Pay"</strong> on the home screen, then select <strong>"Show My QR Code"</strong>. Your personal payment QR code will be displayed.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </li>
                                <li class="cmp-step">
                                    <div class="cmp-step-number">2</div>
                                    <div class="cmp-step-content">
                                        <h5>Present to Merchant</h5>
                                        <p>Hold your phone steady with the QR code visible. The merchant will scan it using their MPay Merchant terminal or device camera.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </li>
                                <li class="cmp-step">
                                    <div class="cmp-step-number">3</div>
                                    <div class="cmp-step-content">
                                        <h5>Confirm on Your Device</h5>
                                        <p>After the merchant scans and enters the amount, you'll receive a push notification. Confirm the payment amount and authenticate to complete.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </li>
                            </ol>
                            <!-- QR Code Display Visual -->
                            <div class="cmp-qr-visual" aria-hidden="true">
                                <div class="cmp-phone-mockup">
                                    <div class="cmp-phone-screen">
                                        <div class="cmp-phone-notch"></div>
                                        <div class="cmp-qr-code-display"></div>
                                        <div class="cmp-qr-label">Show this to merchant</div>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="cmp-callout warning">
                                <div class="cmp-callout-icon">
                                    <i class="fa fa-exclamation-triangle"></i>
                                </div>
                                <div class="cmp-callout-body">
                                    <strong>Security Note</strong>
                                    <p>Your payment QR code refreshes every 60 seconds for security. Never share a screenshot of your QR code. Only show it at the point of sale when making a payment.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </section>
                        <!-- Section: NFC Tap-to-Pay -->
                        <section class="cmp-section" id="cmp_content_nfc_tap">
                            <h2 class="cmp-section-title" id="nfc-tap">NFC Tap-to-Pay</h2>
                            <p>If your device supports NFC and the merchant has an NFC-enabled terminal, you can pay by simply tapping your phone against their payment device — no scanning needed.</p>
                            <h4>How to Use NFC Payments</h4>
                            <ol class="cmp-steps">
                                <li class="cmp-step">
                                    <div class="cmp-step-number">1</div>
                                    <div class="cmp-step-content">
                                        <h5>Enable NFC</h5>
                                        <p>Ensure NFC is enabled in your phone settings and in the MPay app under <strong>Settings → Payment Methods → NFC Payments</strong>.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </li>
                                <li class="cmp-step">
                                    <div class="cmp-step-number">2</div>
                                    <div class="cmp-step-content">
                                        <h5>Hold Near Terminal</h5>
                                        <p>When the merchant's terminal shows the amount, hold the back of your phone (near the NFC antenna) within 4cm of the payment terminal.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </li>
                                <li class="cmp-step">
                                    <div class="cmp-step-number">3</div>
                                    <div class="cmp-step-content">
                                        <h5>Authenticate</h5>
                                        <p>A vibration or tone confirms the connection. Authenticate using biometrics or your PIN. The payment processes in under 2 seconds.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </li>
                                <li class="cmp-step">
                                    <div class="cmp-step-number">4</div>
                                    <div class="cmp-step-content">
                                        <h5>Payment Complete</h5>
                                        <p>You'll see a success checkmark and receive both an in-app notification and optional SMS receipt.</p>
                                    </div>
                                </li>
                            </ol>
                            <!-- NFC Visual Animation -->
                            <div class="cmp-nfc-visual" aria-hidden="true">
                                <div class="cmp-nfc-device">
                                    <div class="cmp-nfc-icon-container">
                                        <i class="fa fa-mobile-alt"></i>
                                        <div class="cmp-nfc-wave"></div>
                                        <div class="cmp-nfc-wave"></div>
                                        <div class="cmp-nfc-wave"></div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="cmp-nfc-label">Your Phone</div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="cmp-nfc-arrow">
                                    <i class="fa fa-chevron-right"></i>
                                    <i class="fa fa-chevron-right"></i>
                                    <i class="fa fa-chevron-right"></i>
                                </div>
                                <div class="cmp-nfc-device">
                                    <div class="cmp-nfc-icon-container">
                                        <i class="fa fa-cash-register"></i>
                                        <div class="cmp-nfc-wave"></div>
                                        <div class="cmp-nfc-wave"></div>
                                        <div class="cmp-nfc-wave"></div>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="cmp-nfc-label">Payment Terminal</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="cmp-callout info">
                                <div class="cmp-callout-icon">
                                    <i class="fa fa-info-circle"></i>
                                </div>
                                <div class="cmp-callout-body">
                                    <strong>NFC Antenna Location</strong>
                                    <p>The NFC antenna is usually located at the top-center of the back of your phone. Remove thick phone cases if you're having trouble connecting. Check your device manufacturer's specs for exact antenna placement.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </section>
                        <!-- Section: Payment Confirmation -->
                        <section class="cmp-section" id="cmp_content_confirm">
                            <h2 class="cmp-section-title" id="payment-confirmation">Payment Confirmation</h2>
                            <p>After every successful payment, you'll receive an instant confirmation with transaction details. This serves as your digital receipt.</p>
                            <h4>What's Included in Your Receipt</h4>
                            <p>Every payment confirmation includes the following details:</p>
                            <!-- Receipt Mock -->
                            <div class="cmp-receipt-mock" aria-label="Example payment receipt">
                                <div class="cmp-receipt-icon">
                                    <i class="fa fa-check-circle"></i>
                                </div>
                                <div class="cmp-receipt-label">Payment Successful</div>
                                <div class="cmp-receipt-amount">XCG42.50</div>
                                <div class="cmp-receipt-label">Coffee House Downtown</div>
                                <div class="cmp-receipt-details">
                                    <div class="cmp-receipt-row">
                                        <span class="label">Transaction ID</span>
                                        <span class="value">#MPY-2025-8A3F</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="cmp-receipt-row">
                                        <span class="label">Date & Time</span>
                                        <span class="value">Mar 11, 2025 • 2:34 PM</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="cmp-receipt-row">
                                        <span class="label">Payment Method</span>
                                        <span class="value">QR Code</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="cmp-receipt-row">
                                        <span class="label">Status</span>
                                        <span class="value" style="color: #22c55e; font-weight: 600;">Completed</span>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="cmp-receipt-row">
                                        <span class="label">Wallet Balance</span>
                                        <span class="value">XCG 1,457.50</span>
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="cmp-callout success">
                                <div class="cmp-callout-icon">
                                    <i class="fa fa-check-circle"></i>
                                </div>
                                <div class="cmp-callout-body">
                                    <strong>Share & Export Receipts</strong>
                                    <p>Tap the <strong>"Share"</strong> button on any receipt to send it via email, messaging apps, or save as a PDF. You can also export all receipts from the Transaction History section for accounting purposes.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <h4>Failed or Pending Payments</h4>
                            <p>If a payment fails or remains pending, you'll see a different status screen:</p>
                            <ul style="margin: 12px 0 16px 20px; color: #334155; line-height: 1.8;">
                                <li>
                                    <strong style="color: #d97706;">Pending:</strong> The payment is being processed. This usually resolves within 30 seconds. Don't retry until it resolves.
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <strong style="color: #dc2626;">Failed:</strong> The payment could not be completed. Check your balance, internet connection, and try again. No money is deducted for failed transactions.
                                </li>
                                <li>
                                    <strong style="color: #2563eb;">Refunded:</strong> The merchant initiated a refund. Funds return to your wallet within 1-3 business days.
                                </li>
                            </ul>
                        </section>
                        <!-- Section: Payment History -->
                        <section class="cmp-section" id="cmp_content_history">
                            <h2 class="cmp-section-title" id="payment-history">Transaction History</h2>
                            <p>Track all your past payments in one place. Your transaction history keeps a complete record of every payment you&apos;ve made through the mPay Consumer Wallet.</p>
                            <h4>Accessing Your History</h4>
                            <p>Navigate to <strong>Home → Transactions</strong> or swipe up on the home screen. You can filter transactions by date range, payment method, status, or merchant name.</p>
                            <h4>Sample Transaction History</h4>
                            <div class="cmp-history-table-wrapper">
                                <table class="cmp-history-table" aria-label="Sample transaction history">
                                    <thead>
                                        <tr>
                                            <th>Date</th>
                                            <th>Merchant</th>
                                            <th>Method</th>
                                            <th>Amount</th>
                                            <th>Status</th>
                                        </tr>
                                    </thead>
                                    <tbody>
                                        <tr>
                                            <td>Mar 11, 2025</td>
                                            <td>Coffee House Downtown</td>
                                            <td><span class="cmp-method-icon"><i class="fa fa-qrcode"></i> QR Code</span></td>
                                            <td>XCG 42.50</td>
                                            <td><span class="cmp-status-badge completed"><i class="fa fa-check-circle"></i> Completed</span></td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr>
                                            <td>Mar 10, 2025</td>
                                            <td>QuickMart Grocery</td>
                                            <td><span class="cmp-method-icon"><i class="fa fa-wifi"></i> NFC</span></td>
                                            <td>XCG 128.75</td>
                                            <td><span class="cmp-status-badge completed"><i class="fa fa-check-circle"></i> Completed</span></td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr>
                                            <td>Mar 10, 2025</td>
                                            <td>Metro Gas Station</td>
                                            <td><span class="cmp-method-icon"><i class="fa fa-qrcode"></i> QR Code</span></td>
                                            <td>XCG 55.00</td>
                                            <td><span class="cmp-status-badge completed"><i class="fa fa-check-circle"></i> Completed</span></td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr>
                                            <td>Mar 9, 2025</td>
                                            <td>TechShop Online</td>
                                            <td><span class="cmp-method-icon"><i class="fa fa-qrcode"></i> QR Code</span></td>
                                            <td>XCG 299.99</td>
                                            <td><span class="cmp-status-badge pending"><i class="fa fa-clock"></i> Pending</span></td>
                                        </tr>
                                        <tr>
                                            <td>Mar 8, 2025</td>
                                            <td>City Pharmacy</td>
                                            <td><span class="cmp-method-icon"><i class="fa fa-wifi"></i> NFC</span></td>
                                            <td>XCG 18.30</td>
                                            <td><span class="cmp-status-badge completed"><i class="fa fa-check-circle"></i> Completed</span></td>
                                        </tr>
                                    </tbody>
                                </table>
                            </div>
                            <div class="cmp-callout info">
                                <div class="cmp-callout-icon">
                                    <i class="fa fa-info-circle"></i>
                                </div>
                                <div class="cmp-callout-body">
                                    <strong>Export Your Data</strong>
                                    <p>You can export your transaction history as CSV or PDF by tapping the <strong>"Export"</strong> button at the top of the Transactions screen. Choose a date range and file format.</p>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </section>
                        <!-- Payment Flow Screenshots -->
                        <section class="cmp-screenshots-section" id="cmp_screenshots">
                            <h2 class="cmp-section-title" id="payment-flow">Payment Flow Overview</h2>
                            <p>Here's a visual walkthrough of the complete payment process from start to finish.</p>
                            <div class="cmp-screenshots-grid">
                                <div class="cmp-screenshot-card">
                                    <div class="cmp-screenshot-image">
                                        <span class="cmp-screenshot-step-badge">Step 1</span>
                                        <i class="fa fa-hand-pointer"></i>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="cmp-screenshot-caption">Tap "Pay" on home screen</div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="cmp-screenshot-card">
                                    <div class="cmp-screenshot-image">
                                        <span class="cmp-screenshot-step-badge">Step 2</span>
                                        <i class="fa fa-qrcode"></i>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="cmp-screenshot-caption">Choose QR scan or NFC tap</div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="cmp-screenshot-card">
                                    <div class="cmp-screenshot-image">
                                        <span class="cmp-screenshot-step-badge">Step 3</span>
                                        <i class="fa fa-camera"></i>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="cmp-screenshot-caption">Scan merchant QR code</div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="cmp-screenshot-card">
                                    <div class="cmp-screenshot-image">
                                        <span class="cmp-screenshot-step-badge">Step 4</span>
                                        <i class="fa fa-dollar-sign"></i>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="cmp-screenshot-caption">Review payment amount</div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="cmp-screenshot-card">
                                    <div class="cmp-screenshot-image">
                                        <span class="cmp-screenshot-step-badge">Step 5</span>
                                        <i class="fa fa-fingerprint"></i>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="cmp-screenshot-caption">Authenticate with biometrics</div>
                                </div>
                                <div class="cmp-screenshot-card">
                                    <div class="cmp-screenshot-image">
                                        <span class="cmp-screenshot-step-badge">Step 6</span>
                                        <i class="fa fa-check-circle"></i>
                                    </div>
                                    <div class="cmp-screenshot-caption">Payment confirmed!</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </section>
                        <!-- FAQ Section -->
                        <section class="cmp-faq-section" id="cmp_faq_accordion">
                            <h2 class="cmp-section-title" id="faq">Frequently Asked Questions</h2>
                            <div class="cmp-faq-item">
                                <button class="cmp-faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-answer-1">
                                    <span>What's the maximum amount I can pay per transaction?</span>
                                    <i class="fa fa-chevron-down"></i>
                                </button>
                                <div class="cmp-faq-answer" id="faq-answer-1" role="region">
                                    <div class="cmp-faq-answer-inner">
                                        The default transaction limit is $5,000 per payment. Verified accounts (KYC Level 2) can request higher limits up to $25,000 per transaction. You can view and manage your limits in <strong>Settings → Payment Limits</strong>.
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="cmp-faq-item">
                                <button class="cmp-faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-answer-2">
                                    <span>Can I pay without an internet connection?</span>
                                    <i class="fa fa-chevron-down"></i>
                                </button>
                                <div class="cmp-faq-answer" id="faq-answer-2" role="region">
                                    <div class="cmp-faq-answer-inner">
                                        NFC payments can work in offline mode for small transactions (under $50) if you have pre-authorized offline payments in your settings. QR code payments always require an active internet connection to process. Offline payments sync once you're back online.
</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="cmp-faq-item">
                                <button class="cmp-faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-answer-3">
                                    <span>What should I do if the QR scanner doesn't recognize the code?</span>
                                    <i class="fa fa-chevron-down"></i>
                                </button>
                                <div class="cmp-faq-answer" id="faq-answer-3" role="region">
                                    <div class="cmp-faq-answer-inner">
                                        First, ensure you have adequate lighting and hold your camera steady. Clean your camera lens if it's smudged. If the QR code appears damaged or faded, ask the merchant to generate a fresh code. You can also try entering the merchant's payment ID manually by tapping "Enter Code Manually" below the scanner.
</div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="cmp-faq-item">
                                <button class="cmp-faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-answer-4">
                                    <span>Is NFC payment supported on all devices?</span>
                                    <i class="fa fa-chevron-down"></i>
                                </button>
                                <div class="cmp-faq-answer" id="faq-answer-4" role="region">
                                    <div class="cmp-faq-answer-inner">
                                        NFC payments require a device with an NFC chip. Most Android phones manufactured after 2018 and all iPhones from iPhone 7 onwards support NFC. You can check compatibility in <strong>Settings → Payment Methods → NFC Status</strong>. If your device doesn't support NFC, you can still use QR code payments.
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="cmp-faq-item">
                                <button class="cmp-faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-answer-5">
                                    <span>Are there any fees for making payments?</span>
                                    <i class="fa fa-chevron-down"></i>
                                </button>
                                <div class="cmp-faq-answer" id="faq-answer-5" role="region">
                                    <div class="cmp-faq-answer-inner">
                                        MPay Consumer Wallet does not charge any fees for making payments to merchants. The payment processing fee is handled on the merchant's side. P2P transfers may have a small fee depending on your account tier — check the <a onclick="load_page('consumer_p2p_transfers')" style="color: #2563eb; cursor: pointer; text-decoration: underline;">P2P Transfers</a> documentation for details.
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                            <div class="cmp-faq-item">
                                <button class="cmp-faq-question" aria-expanded="false" aria-controls="faq-answer-6">
                                    <span>Can I cancel a payment after it's been sent?</span>
                                    <i class="fa fa-chevron-down"></i>
                                </button>
                                <div class="cmp-faq-answer" id="faq-answer-6" role="region">
                                    <div class="cmp-faq-answer-inner">
                                        Completed payments cannot be cancelled directly. You'll need to contact the merchant and request a refund through the MPay system. If you believe a payment was unauthorized, go to <strong>Transactions → Select Transaction → Report Issue</strong> to initiate a dispute. Our support team responds within 24 hours.
                                    </div>
                                </div>
                            </div>
                        </section>
                        <!-- Prev / Next Navigation -->
                        <nav class="cmp-prev-next" id="cmp_prev_next" aria-label="Page navigation">
